LanguageData.CAN_CannibalKibble.label: cannibal kibble
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalKibble.description: Animal feed made from human and plant sources. Humans can eat it, but they really, really don't like it.
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealFine.label: cannibal fine meal
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealFine.description: A complex dish assembled with care from human meat and a wide selection of ingredients.
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealLavish.label: cannibal lavish meal
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealLavish.description: A masterpiece of the cannibal culinary arts, this meal nourishes the body, mind, and soul.
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealSimple.label: cannibal simple meal
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealSimple.description: A simple meal quickly cooked from human meat and a few ingredients.
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealSurvivalPack.label: cannibal packaged survival meal
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalMealSurvivalPack.description: A high-quality cannibal packaged meal, manufactured for use in survival situations.
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalPemmican.label: cannibal pemmican
LanguageData.CAN_CannibalPemmican.description: A preserved mashed mixture of human fat and plant food. Tastes bland, but not offensive. It lasts a very long time without refrigeration.
